{
  "video_id": "Fg_JcKSHUtQ",
  "title": "A robot that flies like a bird | Markus Fischer",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 15895.0,
      "end_time": 20142.0,
      "text": "It is a dream of mankind to fly like a bird."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 20166.0,
      "end_time": 22236.0,
      "text": "Birds are very agile."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 22260.0,
      "end_time": 25594.0,
      "text": "They fly, not with rotating components,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 25618.0,
      "end_time": 28674.0,
      "text": "so they fly only by flapping their wings."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 29230.0,
      "end_time": 31236.0,
      "text": "So we looked at the birds,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 31260.0,
      "end_time": 37603.0,
      "text": "and we tried to make a model that is powerful, ultralight,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 37627.0,
      "end_time": 41641.0,
      "text": "and it must have excellent aerodynamic qualities"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 41665.0,
      "end_time": 45772.0,
      "text": "that would fly by its own and only by flapping its wings."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 46400.0,
      "end_time": 51236.0,
      "text": "So what would be better than to use the herring gull, in its freedom,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 51260.0,
      "end_time": 53574.0,
      "text": "circling and swooping over the sea,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 53598.0,
      "end_time": 56423.0,
      "text": "and to use this as a role model?"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 56937.0,
      "end_time": 58897.0,
      "text": "So we bring a team together."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 58921.0,
      "end_time": 64100.0,
      "text": "There are generalists and also specialists in the field of aerodynamics,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 64250.0,
      "end_time": 66236.0,
      "text": "in the field of building gliders."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 66589.0,
      "end_time": 71962.0,
      "text": "And the task was to build an ultralight indoor-flying model"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 71986.0,
      "end_time": 75163.0,
      "text": "that is able to fly over your heads."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 75187.0,
      "end_time": 77259.0,
      "text": "So be careful later on."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 77745.0,
      "end_time": 79387.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 80770.0,
      "end_time": 81521.0,
      "text": "And this was one issue:"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 81545.0,
      "end_time": 83237.0,
      "text": "to build it that lightweight"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 83261.0,
      "end_time": 88920.0,
      "text": "that no one would be hurt if it fell down."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 88648.0,
      "end_time": 90600.0,
      "text": "So why do we do all this?"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 90624.0,
      "end_time": 93547.0,
      "text": "We are a company in the field of automation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 93571.0,
      "end_time": 96236.0,
      "text": "and we&#39;d like to do very lightweight structures"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 96260.0,
      "end_time": 98999.0,
      "text": "because that&#39;s energy efficient,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 99230.0,
      "end_time": 104666.0,
      "text": "and we&#39;d like to learn more about pneumatics and air flow phenomena."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 105111.0,
      "end_time": 109538.0,
      "text": "So I now would like you to put your seat belts on"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 109562.0,
      "end_time": 111236.0,
      "text": "and put your hats on."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 111799.0,
      "end_time": 114875.0,
      "text": "So maybe we&#39;ll try it once --"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 114899.0,
      "end_time": 116379.0,
      "text": "to fly a SmartBird."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 116403.0,
      "end_time": 117431.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 117455.0,
      "end_time": 124346.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 133888.0,
      "end_time": 135134.0,
      "text": "(Cheers)"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 135158.0,
      "end_time": 138542.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 149328.0,
      "end_time": 151218.0,
      "text": "(Applause ends)"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 171268.0,
      "end_time": 174417.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 187705.0,
      "end_time": 192420.0,
      "text": "So we can now look at the SmartBird."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 193840.0,
      "end_time": 195566.0,
      "text": "So here is one without a skin."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 195590.0,
      "end_time": 198801.0,
      "text": "We have a wingspan of about two meters."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 198825.0,
      "end_time": 201236.0,
      "text": "The length is one meter and six,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 201260.0,
      "end_time": 205447.0,
      "text": "and the weight is only 450 grams."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 206530.0,
      "end_time": 209236.0,
      "text": "And it is all out of carbon fiber."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 209260.0,
      "end_time": 211719.0,
      "text": "In the middle we have a motor,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 211743.0,
      "end_time": 215236.0,
      "text": "and we also have a gear in it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 215260.0,
      "end_time": 220875.0,
      "text": "and we use the gear to transfer the circulation of the motor."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 220899.0,
      "end_time": 224850.0,
      "text": "So within the motor, we have three Hall sensors,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 224109.0,
      "end_time": 227622.0,
      "text": "so we know exactly where the wing is."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 229710.0,
      "end_time": 232711.0,
      "text": "And if we now beat up and down --"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 232735.0,
      "end_time": 236672.0,
      "text": "(Mechanical sounds)"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 236696.0,
      "end_time": 240759.0,
      "text": "We have the possibility to fly like a bird."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 240783.0,
      "end_time": 244400.0,
      "text": "So if you go down, you have the large area of propulsion,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 244425.0,
      "end_time": 247512.0,
      "text": "and if you go up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 247536.0,
      "end_time": 250236.0,
      "text": "the wings are not that large,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 250260.0,
      "end_time": 253260.0,
      "text": "and it is easier to get up."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 255129.0,
      "end_time": 258176.0,
      "text": "So, the next thing we did,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 258200.0,
      "end_time": 259973.0,
      "text": "or the challenges we did,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 259997.0,
      "end_time": 263130.0,
      "text": "was to coordinate this movement."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 263370.0,
      "end_time": 266226.0,
      "text": "We have to turn it, go up and go down."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 266250.0,
      "end_time": 267786.0,
      "text": "We have a split wing."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 267810.0,
      "end_time": 269236.0,
      "text": "With the split wing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 269260.0,
      "end_time": 272236.0,
      "text": "we get the lift at the upper wing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 272260.0,
      "end_time": 275474.0,
      "text": "and we get the propulsion at the lower wing."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 275498.0,
      "end_time": 280716.0,
      "text": "Also, we see how we measure the aerodynamic efficiency."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 280740.0,
      "end_time": 284970.0,
      "text": "We had knowledge about the electromechanical efficiency"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 284994.0,
      "end_time": 288952.0,
      "text": "and then we can calculate the aerodynamic efficiency."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 288976.0,
      "end_time": 294296.0,
      "text": "So therefore, it rises up from passive torsion to active torsion,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 294320.0,
      "end_time": 296883.0,
      "text": "from 30 percent up to 80 percent."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 297581.0,
      "end_time": 299440.0,
      "text": "Next thing we have to do,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 299464.0,
      "end_time": 303565.0,
      "text": "we have to control and regulate the whole structure."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 303589.0,
      "end_time": 306160.0,
      "text": "Only if you control and regulate it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 306184.0,
      "end_time": 309477.0,
      "text": "you will get that aerodynamic efficiency."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 309501.0,
      "end_time": 312587.0,
      "text": "So the overall consumption of energy"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 312612.0,
      "end_time": 315816.0,
      "text": "is about 25 watts at takeoff"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 315840.0,
      "end_time": 319371.0,
      "text": "and 16 to 18 watts in flight."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 319396.0,
      "end_time": 320405.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 320429.0,
      "end_time": 327100.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 327340.0,
      "end_time": 329582.0,
      "text": "Bruno Giussani: Markus, we should fly it once more."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 329606.0,
      "end_time": 331100.0,
      "text": "Markus Fischer: Yeah, sure."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 331350.0,
      "end_time": 332103.0,
      "text": "(Audience) Yeah!"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 332127.0,
      "end_time": 333728.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 353383.0,
      "end_time": 357990.0,
      "text": "(Gasps)"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 362690.0,
      "end_time": 363863.0,
      "text": "(Cheers)"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 363887.0,
      "end_time": 366990.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}